<idea-plugin>
    <id>com.github.idea-claude-code-gui</id>
    <name>CC GUI（Claude or Codex）</name>
    <vendor>MossX</vendor>

    <!-- Resource bundle for i18n -->
    <resource-bundle>messages.ClaudeCodeGuiBundle</resource-bundle>

    <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>Dual-engine GUI for Claude Code and Codex - MIT 100% Open Source</h2>
        <h2>Claude Code 和 Codex 的双引擎GUI MIT 100%开源产品</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Claude Code</strong> Anthropic 官方 AI 编程助手（支持 Opus 4.6 等多模型）</li>
            <li><strong>OpenAI Codex</strong> - OpenAI 强大的代码生成引擎</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Connection &amp; proxy disclosure / 连接与代理说明：</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>By default, requests are sent <strong>directly</strong> to the official Anthropic API (or OpenAI API for Codex).</li>
            <li>Users may optionally configure a third-party or proxy endpoint in <em>Provider Settings</em>. When a non-official base URL is set, the plugin UI clearly labels the request route as proxied <strong>before</strong> it is used.</li>
            <li>Users can freely switch between direct and proxy modes at any time in the provider settings.</li>
            <li>Only when users explicitly enable <em>Local settings.json</em> or <em>CLI Login</em> mode, the plugin may honor network proxy variables from <code>~/.claude/settings.json</code> (e.g. <code>HTTP_PROXY</code>, <code>HTTPS_PROXY</code>) for API requests. Managed provider presets do not silently inherit these local proxy variables.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>默认情况下，请求直接发送到 Anthropic（或 OpenAI）官方 API。用户可在供应商设置中选配第三方或代理端点，插件 UI 会在使用前明确标注请求路由方式。用户可随时在直连与代理模式间自由切换。只有当用户显式启用“本地 settings.json”或“CLI Login”模式时，插件才可能继承 <code>~/.claude/settings.json</code> 中的网络代理变量（如 HTTP_PROXY、HTTPS_PROXY）；普通托管供应商预设不会静默继承这些本地代理变量。</p>

        <p><strong>Credential &amp; file-access disclosure / 凭证与文件访问说明：</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>No silent credential scanning.</strong> The plugin never silently scans your disk for API keys or tokens. All credential sources require <strong>explicit user authorization</strong> via a confirmation dialog in the plugin UI.</li>
            <li><strong>Provider credentials</strong>: Users enter API keys manually in the provider settings UI, or explicitly authorize reading from <code>~/.claude/settings.json</code>, or explicitly authorize delegating to the Claude SDK's native OAuth flow (CLI Login). If Claude provider access is revoked or disabled, the plugin does not continue using credentials from <code>~/.claude/settings.json</code>.</li>
            <li><strong>MCP server configuration</strong>: When the user opens the MCP settings page, the plugin reads MCP server definitions (server names, commands, arguments) from <code>~/.claude.json</code>. This file contains <strong>no credentials or tokens</strong> — only MCP server configuration metadata managed by the Claude CLI.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>插件不会静默扫描磁盘上的凭证。所有凭证来源均需用户在 UI 中显式授权确认。MCP 服务器配置仅在用户打开 MCP 设置页面时读取，该文件仅含服务器定义，不含任何凭证或令牌。</p>

        <h2>核心功能</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>上下文感知助手</strong>：智能编程助手，支持 @文件引用</li>
            <li><strong>图片支持</strong>：发送图片可视化描述需求</li>
            <li><strong>Agent 系统</strong>：内置智能体自动化执行复杂任务</li>
            <li><strong>Skills 命令</strong>：斜杠命令系统（/init, /review 等）</li>
            <li><strong>MCP 服务器</strong>：通过 MCP 协议扩展 AI 能力</li>
            <li><strong>代码 DIFF</strong>：可视化代码对比和文件导航</li>
            <li><strong>对话回退</strong>：灵活调整对话历史</li>
            <li><strong>会话管理</strong>：历史记录、收藏、搜索和导出</li>
            <li><strong>主题支持</strong>：深色/浅色主题，支持 IDE 字体同步</li>
            <li><strong>权限控制</strong>：完善的安全管理</li>
            <li><strong>供应商管理</strong>：兼容 cc-switch</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>使用方法</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>从右侧边栏打开 CC GUI 工具窗口</li>
            <li>选中代码后使用 <kbd>Ctrl+Alt+K</kbd>（Win/Linux）或 <kbd>Cmd+Alt+K</kbd>（Mac）发送给 AI</li>
            <li>即时获得 AI 驱动的代码辅助和智能建议</li>
        </ul>

        <p><em>Keywords: Claude, Claude Code, Codex, OpenCode, Gemini, Code Generation, AI Coding</em></p>
    ]]></description>

    <depends>com.intellij.modules.platform</depends>
    <!-- Optional: Terminal support for terminal output monitoring -->
    <depends optional="true" config-file="terminal-features.xml">org.jetbrains.plugins.terminal</depends>
    <!-- Optional: Java support for enhanced context collection in Java/Kotlin IDEs -->
    <depends optional="true" config-file="java-features.xml">com.intellij.java</depends>
    <!-- Optional: Python support for enhanced context collection in PyCharm/IDEA with Python plugin -->
    <depends optional="true" config-file="python-features.xml">com.intellij.modules.python</depends>

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <!-- CC GUI tool window (includes history feature) -->
        <toolWindow id="CCG"
                    anchor="right"
                    factoryClass="com.github.claudecodegui.ui.toolwindow.ClaudeSDKToolWindow"
                    icon="/icons/cc-gui-icon.svg"
                    canCloseContents="true"/>

        <!-- Pre-extract AI Bridge on project open to avoid EDT freeze -->
        <postStartupActivity implementation="com.github.claudecodegui.startup.BridgePreloader"/>

        <!-- Cleanup old ai-bridge cache when plugin version changes -->
        <postStartupActivity implementation="com.github.claudecodegui.startup.PluginUpdateListener"/>

        <!-- Monitor Run/Debug Service Output -->
        <postStartupActivity implementation="com.github.claudecodegui.service.RunConfigMonitorService"/>

        <!-- StatusBar widget for task notification -->
        <statusBarWidgetFactory id="ClaudeStatusBarWidget"
                                implementation="com.github.claudecodegui.notifications.ClaudeStatusBarWidget$Factory"/>

        <!-- Notification group for DevTools and other balloon notifications -->
        <notificationGroup id="CC GUI Notifications" displayType="BALLOON"/>
    </extensions>

    <actions>
        <!-- Action to send selected code to CC GUI -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.SendSelectionToTerminalAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.editor.SendSelectionToTerminalAction"
                icon="/icons/send-to-terminal.svg">
            <!-- Add to editor context menu (displayed at the top) -->
            <add-to-group group-id="EditorPopupMenu" anchor="first"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="$default" first-keystroke="ctrl alt K"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="Mac OS X" first-keystroke="meta alt K"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="macOS" first-keystroke="meta alt K"/>
        </action>

        <!-- Copy AI Reference Action -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.CopySelectionReferenceAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.editor.CopySelectionReferenceAction"
                icon="/icons/cc-gui-icon.svg">
            <add-to-group group-id="EditorPopupMenu"
                           anchor="after"
                           relative-to-action="ClaudeCodeGUI.SendSelectionToTerminalAction"/>
        </action>

        <!-- Quick Fix with Claude Action -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.QuickFixWithClaudeAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.editor.QuickFixWithClaudeAction"
                icon="/icons/quick-fix.svg">
            <add-to-group group-id="EditorPopupMenu"
                           anchor="after"
                           relative-to-action="ClaudeCodeGUI.SendSelectionToTerminalAction"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="$default" first-keystroke="ctrl shift Q"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="Mac OS X" first-keystroke="meta shift Q"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="macOS" first-keystroke="meta shift Q"/>
        </action>

        <!-- Create New Tab Action (can be invoked via Find Action or programmatically) -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.CreateNewTabAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.tab.CreateNewTabAction"
                icon="AllIcons.General.Add"/>

        <!-- Rename Tab Action -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.RenameTabAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.tab.RenameTabAction"
                icon="AllIcons.Actions.Edit"/>

        <!-- Detach Tab Action -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.DetachTabAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.tab.DetachTabAction"
                icon="AllIcons.Actions.MoveToWindow"/>

        <!-- Open DevTools Action for JCEF debugging -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.OpenDevToolsAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.dev.OpenDevToolsAction"
                icon="AllIcons.Xml.Browsers.Chromium"/>

        <!-- Action to send file path from the file tree to the input box -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.SendFilePathToInputAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.editor.SendFilePathToInputAction"
                icon="/icons/cc-gui-icon.svg">
            <!-- Add to project file tree and editor tab context menus -->
            <add-to-group group-id="ProjectViewPopupMenu" anchor="first"/>
            <add-to-group group-id="EditorTabPopupMenu" anchor="first"/>
        </action>

        <!-- Action to send the selected console text to CC GUI -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.SendConsoleSelectionToInputAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.console.SendConsoleSelectionToInputAction"
                icon="/icons/cc-gui-icon.svg">
            <add-to-group group-id="ConsoleView.PopupMenu" anchor="last"/>
        </action>

        <!-- Generate Commit Message with AI Action -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.GenerateCommitMessageAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.vcs.GenerateCommitMessageAction"
                icon="/icons/logo-16.png">
            <!-- Add to VCS Commit toolbar -->
            <add-to-group group-id="Vcs.MessageActionGroup" anchor="last"/>
        </action>

        <!-- Chat tool window clipboard actions (scoped to CCG tool window) -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.ChatCopyAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.ChatCopyAction"
                text="Copy (Chat Window)"
                description="Copy selected text in Claude chat window">
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="$default" first-keystroke="ctrl C"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="Mac OS X" first-keystroke="meta C"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="macOS" first-keystroke="meta C"/>
        </action>
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.ChatCutAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.ChatCutAction"
                text="Cut (Chat Window)"
                description="Cut selected text in Claude chat window">
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="$default" first-keystroke="ctrl X"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="Mac OS X" first-keystroke="meta X"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="macOS" first-keystroke="meta X"/>
        </action>
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.ChatPasteAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.ChatPasteAction"
                text="Paste (Chat Window)"
                description="Paste clipboard text in Claude chat window">
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="$default" first-keystroke="ctrl V"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="Mac OS X" first-keystroke="meta V"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="macOS" first-keystroke="meta V"/>
        </action>

        <!-- Chat tool window send action (no default shortcut; dynamically managed by SendShortcutSync) -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.ChatSendAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.ChatSendAction"
                text="Send Message (Chat Window)"
                description="Send message in Claude chat window"/>

        <!-- Chat tool window newline action (Shift+Enter always newline; Ctrl+Enter dynamically managed by SendShortcutSync) -->
        <action id="ClaudeCodeGUI.ChatNewlineAction"
                class="com.github.claudecodegui.action.ChatNewlineAction"
                text="Insert Newline (Chat Window)"
                description="Insert newline in Claude chat window input">
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="$default" first-keystroke="shift ENTER"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="Mac OS X" first-keystroke="shift ENTER"/>
            <keyboard-shortcut keymap="macOS" first-keystroke="shift ENTER"/>
        </action>
    </actions>
</idea-plugin>
